<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:system-ui}
body{background:#f5f7f6;color:#222}

/* HEADER */
.header{
display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
padding:18px 40px;background:#0f6c3f;color:white;
}
.logo{font-weight:bold;font-size:20px}
.nav a{color:white;margin-left:20px;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer}
.donate-btn{background:#ffd54f;color:black;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:6px}

/* PAGES */
.page{display:none;padding:60px 20px;text-align:center}
.active{display:block}

/* HERO */
.hero{
height:80vh;color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.5),rgba(0,0,0,.5)),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588072432836-e10032774350?q=80&w=1200") center/cover;
}
.main-btn{background:#ffd54f;color:black;padding:12px 26px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none}

/* CARDS */
.card{background:white;margin:20px auto;padding:25px;max-width:320px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 5px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}

/* GALLERY */
.gallery img{width:260px;border-radius:12px;margin:10px}

/* FOOTER */
.footer{background:#111;color:#ddd;text-align:center;padding:20px;margin-top:40px}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="header">
<div class="logo">Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</div>
<nav class="nav">
<a onclick="showPage('home')">Home</a>
<a onclick="showPage('about')">About</a>
<a onclick="showPage('gallery')">Gallery</a>
<a onclick="showPage('contact')">Contact</a>
<a onclick="showPage('donate')" class="donate-btn">Donate</a>
</nav>
</header>

<!-- HOME -->
<section id="home" class="page active">
<div class="hero">
<div>
<h1>Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</h1>
<p>तुमचं एक छोटंसं पाऊल, एखाद्या मुलाचं संपूर्ण भविष्य घडवू शकतं.</p>
<br>
<a onclick="showPage('donate')" class="main-btn">Donate Now</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="page">
<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>Yashasvi Foundation अंतर्गत हा उपक्रम गरिब विद्यार्थ्यांना शिक्षण मदत देण्यासाठी आहे.</p>
<div class="card">शैक्षणिक साहित्य</div>
<div class="card">फी सहाय्य</div>
<div class="card">पूर्ण शिक्षण समर्थन</div>
</section>

<!-- GALLERY -->
<section id="gallery" class="page gallery">
<h2>Our Work</h2>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509062522246-3755977927d7?q=80&w=800">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?q=80&w=800">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513258496099-48168024aec0?q=80&w=800">
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section id="contact" class="page">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Yashasvi Foundation</p>
<p>Pankaj Gunjal & Gitesh Ahire</p>
<p>Email: example@gmail.com</p>
</section>

<!-- DONATE -->
<section id="donate" class="page">
<h2>Support Education</h2>
<p>UPI द्वारे मदत करा</p>
<br>
<a href="upi://pay?pa=YOURUPI@upi&pn=Yashasvi%20Foundation&cu=INR" class="main-btn">Pay via UPI</a>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
<p>© Yashasvi Foundation</p>
</footer>

<script>
function showPage(id){
document.querySelectorAll(".page").forEach(p=>p.classList.remove("active"));
document.getElementById(id).classList.add("active");
window.scrollTo(0,0);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
